    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">400+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Valid EX- words</p></div>
    <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">2–15</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Letter length range</p></div>
  </div>
</div>

<p>The X tile on a double or triple letter score with an EX- word can yield 16 or 24 points from that single tile alone. Positioning your EX- play to land X on a premium square is the key to massive scores.</p>

